'''Ali Khencheli''' or '''Mahmoud Djellal''' (born at [[Khenchela]]) is an [[Algerian people|Algerian]] musician of [[Berber people|Berber]] origin.<ref>Algérie.Par Dominique Auzias, Marie-Hélène Martin, Jean-Paul Labourdette
Collaborateur Collectif. Publié par Nouvelles Éditions de l'Université, 2006. {{ISBN|2746917726}} [https://books.google.com/books?id=m094-JowgbwC&pg=PA120&dq=ali+khenchli&sig=xzNqWUGm1AG6RZBnI_S0Fr0OHnk  book on ligne fr]</ref><ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=DgU5AQAAIAAJ&q=ali+khencheli&dq=ali+khencheli&hl=fr&sa=X&ei=W9kaUt2CM6H_4AOzkoHoDg&redir_esc=y  BOOK GOOGLE ENGLISH TEXT]</ref> He singing since 1940 to 1960, he died at 88 years old.

